short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Easily publish your Freelancer profile at Cherry-pick.io platform, and synchronize it with your personal LinkedIn account

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension is part of cherry-pick.io Freelancer and Mission search platform. It allows for easy creating a free-lancer account and to synchronize it with candidate LinkedIn profile.
